@baseUrl = http://localhost:5294

### 1. Login para obtener el token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "erick@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Guarda el token de la respuesta anterior en @token
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 2. Agregar un anime a mi lista (Attack on Titan = MalId 16498)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/anime-list
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "malId": 16498
}

###

### 3. Agregar otro anime (Fullmetal Alchemist Brotherhood = MalId 5114)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/anime-list
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "malId": 5114
}

###

### 4. Ver mi lista completa
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/anime-list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Ver mi lista filtrada por estado (PlanToWatch)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/anime-list?status=PlanToWatch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Actualizar una entrada (reemplaza {entryId} con el id real)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/anime-list/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "watchStatus": "Watching",
  "episodesWatched": 5,
  "score": null,
  "isFavorite": true,
  "startedAt": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "finishedAt": null
}

###

### 7. Eliminar una entrada (reemplaza {entryId} con el id real)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/anime-list/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Sin token — debe devolver 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/anime-list
